<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Rachel Louise Carson</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Rachel-Carson.jpg" class="image" title="Rachel-Carson.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f4/Rachel-Carson.jpg/200px-Rachel-Carson.jpg" width="200" height="253" border="0" /></a><br />
